Author: Zyklar
Text: I think your just not used to it. My thighs jiggled when i recovered and i was still a very low weight compared to others, and they still do even around my lowest. Focus on being thankful for all your legs and ass do for you and also embrace the cake

Author: Saakkkaaaaiiiii
Text: Well I would say it’s completely normal to have ‘jiggly’ parts of your body, no matter what your weight. I wouldn’t worry about it too much dude.
